manthashawhan/video/7624280443961085215", "input": "https://www.tiktok.com/@samanthashawhan/video/7624280443961085215", "cid": "7624497775543780126", "createTime": 1775216806, "createTimeISO": "2026-04-03T11:46:46.000Z", "text": "My 4 year old (she’s almost 5) loves it. She only plays one game though lol my 2.5 year old loves it too, he enjoys the bluey and basketball games.", "diggCount": 0, "likedByAuthor": false, "pinnedByAuthor": false, "repliesToId": null, "replyCommentTotal": 1, "uid": "12847035", "uniqueId": "shesacombs", "avatarThumbnail": "https://p16-common-sign.tiktokcdn-us.com/tos-maliva-avt-0068/7331007154193793030~tplv-tiktokx-cropcenter:100:100.jpg?dr=9640&refresh_token=65398a2d&x-expires=1775754000&x-signature=QwV%2FWZ1ReE4JL8e%2FVNEYJv%2BrcDk%3D&t=4d5b0474&ps=13740610&shp=30310797&shcp=ff37627b&idc=useast8", "mentions": [], "detailedMentions": [], "text_zh": "我 4 岁的女儿（快 5 岁了）很喜欢。她只玩一款游戏，哈哈，我 2.5 岁的儿子也很喜欢，他喜欢 Bluey 和篮球游戏。"}, {"videoWebUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@samanthashawhan/video/7624280443961085215", "submittedVideoUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@samanthashawhan/video/7624280443961085215", "input": "https://www.tiktok.com/@samanthashawhan/video/7624280443961085215", "cid": "7624515131133870878", "createTime": 1775220811, "createTimeISO": "2026-04-03T12:53:31.000Z", "text": "Ehhh my 4 year old almost 5 isn’t impressed. He liked it for about a week and it faded out fast 😩", "diggCount": 0, "likedByAuthor": false, "pinnedByAuthor": false, "repliesToId": null, "replyCommentTotal": 1, "uid": "6844258024740930566", "uniqueId": "patti.may0nnaise", "avatarThumbnail": "https://p19-common-sign.tiktokcdn-us.com/tos-useast8-avt-0068-tx2/3a1f47981d07c281a00507a7884ae183~tplv-tiktokx-cropcenter:100:100.jpg?dr=9640&refresh_token=94d04f6b&x-expires=1775754000&x-signature=h%2Fl2VzZU1UsPSbOV7RXza%2BJjXH0%3D&t=4d5b0474&ps=13740610&shp=30310797&shcp=ff37627b&idc=useast8", "mentions": [], "detailedMentions": [], "text_zh": "呃，我四岁快五岁的儿子没啥兴趣。他玩了一个星期就觉得没意思了，很快就腻了😩"},